title: Hour 3 - Jon Rahm (07-21-20)
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Jon Rahm (07-21-20)
description:
Jon Rahm talks to Dan about how big of an influence Tiger Woods was to him and a lot of other golfers on the tour right now. Jon says that the first time he played with Tiger he could not enjoy it because he was trying to play his best.
